data.meta_description:
4,490 likes, 373 comments - alilandry on July 4, 2023: "As promised Estela singing “Sound of Freedom” 

REPOSTED:
@estela.monteverde 

Sound of Freedom has been a huge part of my life for 5 amazing years now. It’s mind-blowing to see my dad pour his heart and soul into this movie and spread its powerful message. It’s had this incredible impact on me that no other project has ever had before.

I feel so blessed that I was given a chance to do a cover of Sound of Freedom the Official Anthem of the movie

This film is a must-see for everyone. It’s all about a real issue that we need to be aware of. Sound of Freedom is playing in theaters right now, and trust me, you don’t wanna miss out! Grab your tickets at angel.com/tickets and join me in watching this impactful movie.

#2MillionFor2Million #SoundofFreedomMovie #SongsofFreedom".
